	binary. 

2017-09-11  AJM VERSION 6.0.026
	* src/common.F90: In subroutine get_available_file: if the file prefix is
	blank then a default is used.
	* src/num_integrals.F90: Clearer comments in subroutine Chi_rho_w_overlap.
